Class OracleEdge

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.pg.rdbms.OracleElement

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.tinkerpop.blueprints.Edge, com.tinkerpop.blueprints.Element, java.lang.Comparable, MesgConsts, OracleEdgeBase, OracleElementBase

    public class OracleEdge
extends OracleElement
implements OracleEdgeBase, MesgConsts, java.lang.Comparable
    This class implements the Blueprints Edge and Element interface by using an Oracle backend.
